    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Mean relative error on NIH of 8.3% is within the established acceptance threshold. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The credibility evidence package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
